## Current-project batch example

Typical safe parallel wave for this repo:

```
ORCHESTRATION (by ownership)
🟢 PARALLEL (wave-a):
  #— Guidebook seed (feature-agent, ownership: src/lib/guidebook-seed.ts)
  #— Export snapshots (test-agent, ownership: src/lib/epub-export.snapshots.test.ts)
  #— Router rules docs (docs-agent, ownership: .cursor/rules/, docs/agent-router.md)
  #— EPUB import research (docs-agent or feature-agent, ownership: src/lib/epub.ts — read-only investigate)
```

After wave completes: `@merge-manager-agent` → `@review-agent` → `@pr-creator-agent`.

